<li><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="background:white"><span style="font-family:Palatino"><span style="color:black">Ig’s deposit and activate complement: key is C4d staining in the graft will be strongly positive</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>
